sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant KServe as KServe Controller
    participant ODH as ODH Model Controller
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Istio as Istio Gateway<br/>mTLS
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,NGC: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation with Route

    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>KServe: Watch event
    KServe->>Predictor: Create Predictor Pod
    K8sAPI->>ODH: Watch InferenceService
    ODH->>Router: Create OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP
    Predictor->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>AWS credentials
    S3-->>Predictor: Model files

    User->>Router: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token
    Router->>Istio: Forward request<br/>mTLS
    Istio->>Predictor: Inference request<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>mTLS
    Predictor-->>Istio: Prediction result
    Istio-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: JSON response

    Note over User,NGC: Flow 2: NIM Model Serving

    User->>K8sAPI: Create Account CR<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>ODH: Watch Account event
    ODH->>NGC: Retrieve NIM model config<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>API Key
    NGC-->>ODH: Model metadata
    ODH->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap<br/>NIM configuration
    ODH->>K8sAPI: Create/Update InferenceService
    K8sAPI->>KServe: Watch event
    KServe->>Predictor: Create NIM Predictor Pod
    Predictor->>NGC: Download NIM model<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>API Key
    NGC-->>Predictor: NIM model artifacts

    User->>Router: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token
    Router->>Predictor: Forward via Istio<br/>mTLS
    Predictor-->>Router: LLM response
    Router-->>User: JSON response

    Note over User,NGC: Flow 3: LLM InferenceService with Flow Control

    User->>Router: POST /v1/models/llm:predict<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token
    Router->>Istio: Forward request
    Istio->>Istio: AuthorizationPolicy check<br/>Token validation
    Istio->>Predictor: Inference request<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>mTLS
    Predictor->>S3: Load model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>AWS credentials
    S3-->>Predictor: Model files
    Predictor-->>Istio: Prediction result
    Istio-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: JSON response
